[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    130[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m Three-policy fairness re-rank (exposure caps, safety-net floor, near-duplicate suppression) is the right shape, and the framing of fairness as a policy decision calibrated by network operations and compliance (not a hyperparameter) is the framing that will save readers from a foot-gun.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    131[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The label problem is treated honestly: position-bias correction, sparse explicit feedback, downstream signals (calls, bookings, complaints), and provider-side correctness signals are each named and the failure modes called out.[K
