[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    218[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    219[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106mThis is HIGH because the entire fairness-re-rank story depends on windowing being correct, and the recipe's pedagogical focus is on the policy decisions (caps, floors, suppression) not the windowing infrastructure. A reader who builds the cap as the pseudocode shows will produce a system that quietly fails its fairness mission within a few months.[K
