[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    363[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mProblem:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m Not a fix request. Worth flagging that the triple-adverb construction is striking precisely because the rest of the recipe doesn't lean on the same trick. If the editor is tempted to add similar constructions elsewhere for symmetry, resist. This is the right kind of voice flourish: occasional, earned, and load-bearing.[K
