[38;5;141m> [0m{"verdict": "pass", "rationale": "Draft demonstrates strong clinical accuracy with realistic failure modes (laterality flips, hemoptysis/hematemesis confusion, accent disparities, command-vs-content boundary cases) and correct specialty distinctions. Architecture is sound: 8-stage pipeline cleanly separates ASR, command disambiguation, formatting, structured-field extraction, read-edit-sign, and audit; AWS service selection (Transcribe Medical with specialty config, Bedrock for LLM formatting with faithfulness check, Comprehend Medical for coded entity extraction with RxNorm/ICD-10, Step Functions for durable orchestration, WebSocket+REST API Gateway split) is appropriate and HIPAA-eligible. Security posture is rigorous: customer-managed KMS per data class, CloudTrail data events on PHI resources, Object Lock for audit archive, explicit BAA scoping, audio-as-PHI/biometric retention treatment with privacy-officer review, VPC endpoints, least-privilege IAM. The 'Why This Isn't Production-Ready' section functions as prioritized findings: HIGH-priority items (critical-error detection with named clinical ownership, LLM faithfulness program, subgroup-stratified accuracy with disparity alerts, explicit confirmation for structured-field updates, per-clinician adaptation pipeline) include concrete remediation steps; MEDIUM items (voice-command vocabulary versioning, specialty-tuning programs, idempotency/retry, DR/partial-failure handling, EHR integration depth for co-signature/addendum) are actionable; LOW/operational items (cost dashboards, training playbooks, vendor evaluation rigor) are appropriately scoped. TODO verification markers are transparent about unverified claims rather than hidden. Pseudocode is illustrative-grade but accurately reflects Transcribe Medical streaming, Comprehend Medical entity shape, and the read-edit-sign correction-capture loop. Recipe correctly steers toward buy over build for typical institutions and treats the LLM faithfulness risk as structural rather than optional."}[0m[1G[0m[0m[?25h